@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@auth_token = add_token

### Create Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "Java Developer",
  "description": "Develop Spring Boot applications",
  "requirements": "3+ years of experience",
  "salaryMin": 2000,
  "salaryMax": 4000,
  "location": "Ho Chi Minh City",
  "jobType": "full_time"
}

### Get Job by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/{jobId}

### Get All Active Jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs?limit=10&offset=0

### Search Active Jobs by Title
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs?title=Java

### Get All Jobs (Admin/All)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/all

### Search All Jobs by Title
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/all?title=Java

### Update Job
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/{jobId}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "Senior Java Developer",
  "description": "Lead Spring Boot development",
  "requirements": "5+ years of experience",
  "salaryMin": 3000,
  "salaryMax": 6000,
  "location": "Ho Chi Minh City",
  "jobType": "full_time"
}

### Inactivate Job
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/{jobId}/inactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}